1) Installing Virtual Machine and Ubuntu System
2) Installing Ubuntu System "ubuntu-18.04.2-desktop-amd64.iso" on Virtual Machine 
3) Download "qt-opensource-linux-x64-5.14.1.run" from below link: https://qt.mirror.constant.com/archive/qt/
4) Install  "qt-opensource-linux-x64-5.14.1.run"
5) Vitis Development Environment Installation (copy this "Xilinx_Unified_2020.1_0602_1208 " file and install Vitis)
6) Petalinux Tool Installation
